data.description: Gorgeous Home in the Del Webb Mirehaven Gated Community!! This 2208 SF 'Pursuit' has a Beautiful Southwest Exterior Face w/ a Positive Pitch Roof, 2BR's plus an Office/Den, Beautiful Kitchen w/Island, Granite Countertops, Gas Cooktop w/SS Range Hood, Added Cabinets in Kitchen and Laundry, Large Dining Room, & Many Recent Additions including: OWNED Sun State Solar Panels (2021), Newly Remodeled Master Shower w/Tile Surround, Grab Bar & Bench, Luxury Vinyl Flooring in LR & Hall, Tile in Kitchen/Baths, Surround Sound System (Sub Woofer Stays), Window Blinds & Treatments & Ceiling Fans, Front & Back Patio Pavers, Custom Metal Storm Door & Side Gate!  There is a Solar Powered Inverter in the Garage for an EV! All Appliances & Water Softener Convey! SW Bench on the Front Porch stays! SEE MORE!
